body_html: The load data is a feature on the TensorFlow.org version. It probably wouldn't be too hard to enable it in TensorBoard too, but this doesn't feel like a priority. If you want to make a pull request that enables it in TensorBoard be happy to review it. Also pinging @dsmilkov. Marking tensorboard/feature request/contributions welcome.
